oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall household in Nagoya, Japan
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of the Kinsall household standing on the front porch of the Kinsall family home in Nagoya, Japan. From left to right: Yasko (governess and sister to Emiko), Elizabeth Ann Aker (Kinsall's wife and mother to Lucinda and Robert), Emiko (governess and sister to Yasko), Lucinda Kinsall (daughter of Kinsall and Elizabeth, aged 3), unidentified young man (groundskeeper), Robert Yates Kinsall (son of Kinsall and Elizabeth, aged 2).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Kinsall, J.Y.
